{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1343,"text":"For more than 100 years,"},{"time":3096,"text":"the telephone companies have provided\nwiretapping assistance to governments."}]},{"cues":[{"time":7146,"text":"For much of this time,\nthis assistance was manual."},{"time":10708,"text":"Surveillance took place manually\nand wires were connected by hand."},{"time":14850,"text":"Calls were recorded to tape."},{"time":17334,"text":"But as in so many other industries,"},{"time":19502,"text":"computing has changed everything."},{"time":21725,"text":"The telephone companies\nbuilt surveillance features"},{"time":24772,"text":"into the very core of their networks."},{"time":27494,"text":"I want that to sink in for a second:"},{"time":29498,"text":"Our telephones and the networks\nthat carry our calls"},{"time":33782,"text":"were wired for surveillance first."},{"time":36179,"text":"First and foremost."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38763,"text":"So what that means is that\nwhen you're talking to your spouse,"},{"time":42613,"text":"your children, a colleague\nor your doctor on the telephone,"},{"time":46959,"text":"someone could be listening."},{"time":48901,"text":"Now, that someone might\nbe your own government;"},{"time":51490,"text":"it could also be another government,\na foreign intelligence service,"},{"time":55677,"text":"or a hacker, or a criminal, or a stalker"},{"time":58528,"text":"or any other party that breaks into\nthe surveillance system,"},{"time":62122,"text":"that hacks into the surveillance system\nof the telephone companies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67834,"text":"But while the telephone companies\nhave built surveillance as a priority,"},{"time":72380,"text":"Silicon Valley companies have not."},{"time":74523,"text":"And increasingly,\nover the last couple years,"},{"time":77066,"text":"Silicon Valley companies have built\nstrong encryption technology"},{"time":80752,"text":"into their communications products"},{"time":82714,"text":"that makes surveillance\nextremely difficult."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85416,"text":"For example, many of you\nmight have an iPhone,"},{"time":87614,"text":"and if you use an iPhone\nto send a text message"},{"time":90328,"text":"to other people who have an iPhone,"},{"time":92529,"text":"those text messages\ncannot easily be wiretapped."},{"time":95563,"text":"And in fact, according to Apple,"},{"time":97415,"text":"they're not able to even see\nthe text messages themselves."},{"time":100662,"text":"Likewise, if you use FaceTime\nto make an audio call"},{"time":104552,"text":"or a video call with one of your\nfriends or loved ones,"},{"time":107187,"text":"that, too, cannot be easily wiretapped."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109340,"text":"And it's not just Apple."},{"time":111315,"text":"WhatsApp, which is now owned by Facebook"},{"time":113691,"text":"and used by hundreds of millions\nof people around the world,"},{"time":116573,"text":"also has built strong\nencryption technology into its product,"},{"time":120104,"text":"which means that people\nin the Global South can easily communicate"},{"time":123635,"text":"without their governments,\noften authoritarian,"},{"time":126469,"text":"wiretapping their text messages."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129599,"text":"So, after 100 years of being able\nto listen to any telephone call --"},{"time":134568,"text":"anytime, anywhere --"},{"time":137146,"text":"you might imagine that government\nofficials are not very happy."},{"time":140301,"text":"And in fact, that's what's happening."},{"time":142111,"text":"Government officials are extremely mad."},{"time":144354,"text":"And they're not mad because\nthese encryption tools are now available."},{"time":148253,"text":"What upsets them the most"},{"time":150095,"text":"is that the tech companies have built\nencryption features into their products"},{"time":154286,"text":"and turned them on by default."},{"time":156547,"text":"It's the default piece that matters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158541,"text":"In short, the tech companies\nhave democratized encryption."},{"time":163165,"text":"And so, government officials\nlike British Prime Minister David Cameron,"},{"time":166986,"text":"they believe that all communications --\nemails, texts, voice calls --"},{"time":171857,"text":"all of these should be\navailable to governments,"},{"time":174469,"text":"and encryption is making that difficult."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177478,"text":"Now, look -- I'm extremely sympathetic\nto their point of view."},{"time":180886,"text":"We live in a dangerous time\nin a dangerous world,"},{"time":183442,"text":"and there really are bad people out there."},{"time":185466,"text":"There are terrorists and other\nserious national security threats"},{"time":188605,"text":"that I suspect we all want\nthe FBI and the NSA to monitor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193345,"text":"But those surveillance\nfeatures come at a cost."},{"time":197357,"text":"The reason for that is"},{"time":198536,"text":"that there is no such thing\nas a terrorist laptop,"},{"time":201046,"text":"or a drug dealer's cell phone."},{"time":202902,"text":"We all use the same\ncommunications devices."},{"time":206577,"text":"What that means is that\nif the drug dealers' telephone calls"},{"time":210276,"text":"or the terrorists' telephone calls\ncan be intercepted,"},{"time":212845,"text":"then so can the rest of ours, too."},{"time":214865,"text":"And I think we really need to ask:"},{"time":216516,"text":"Should a billion people\naround the world be using devices"},{"time":219667,"text":"that are wiretap friendly?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":223407,"text":"So the scenario of hacking of surveillance\nsystems that I've described --"},{"time":227179,"text":"this is not imaginary."},{"time":229622,"text":"In 2009,"},{"time":230798,"text":"the surveillance systems that Google\nand Microsoft built into their networks --"},{"time":234869,"text":"the systems that they use to respond\nto lawful surveillance requests"},{"time":238384,"text":"from the police --"},{"time":239574,"text":"those systems were compromised\nby the Chinese government,"},{"time":242266,"text":"because the Chinese government\nwanted to figure out"},{"time":244687,"text":"which of their own agents\nthe US government was monitoring."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248269,"text":"By the same token,"},{"time":249564,"text":"in 2004, the surveillance system\nbuilt into the network"},{"time":253007,"text":"of Vodafone Greece --\nGreece's largest telephone company --"},{"time":256205,"text":"was compromised by an unknown entity,"},{"time":258808,"text":"and that feature,\nthe surveillance feature,"},{"time":260872,"text":"was used to wiretap\nthe Greek Prime Minister"},{"time":263174,"text":"and members of the Greek cabinet."},{"time":265313,"text":"The foreign government or hackers\nwho did that were never caught."}]},{"cues":[{"time":269955,"text":"And really, this gets to the very problem\nwith these surveillance features,"},{"time":273676,"text":"or backdoors."},{"time":274960,"text":"When you build a backdoor\ninto a communications network"},{"time":278186,"text":"or piece of technology,"},{"time":279511,"text":"you have no way of controlling\nwho's going to go through it."},{"time":283243,"text":"You have no way of controlling"},{"time":284712,"text":"whether it'll be used by your side\nor the other side,"},{"time":287506,"text":"by good guys, or by bad guys."}]},{"cues":[{"time":289980,"text":"And so for that reason,\nI think that it's better"},{"time":292523,"text":"to build networks\nto be as secure as possible."},{"time":296271,"text":"Yes, this means that in the future,"},{"time":298704,"text":"encryption is going to make\nwiretapping more difficult."},{"time":301280,"text":"It means that the police\nare going to have a tougher time"},{"time":303949,"text":"catching bad guys."},{"time":305309,"text":"But the alternative would mean\nto live in a world"},{"time":307889,"text":"where anyone's calls or anyone's\ntext messages could be surveilled"},{"time":311544,"text":"by criminals, by stalkers\nand by foreign intelligence agencies."},{"time":315294,"text":"And I don't want to live\nin that kind of world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318102,"text":"And so right now,\nyou probably have the tools"},{"time":320841,"text":"to thwart many kinds\nof government surveillance"},{"time":323183,"text":"already on your phones\nand already in your pockets,"},{"time":326190,"text":"you just might not realize how strong\nand how secure those tools are,"},{"time":329993,"text":"or how weak the other ways\nyou've used to communicate really are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334737,"text":"And so, my message to you is this:"},{"time":338110,"text":"We need to use these tools."},{"time":340239,"text":"We need to secure our telephone calls."},{"time":342567,"text":"We need to secure our text messages."},{"time":344950,"text":"I want you to use these tools."},{"time":346626,"text":"I want you to tell your loved ones,\nI want you to tell your colleagues:"},{"time":350006,"text":"Use these encrypted communications tools."},{"time":352454,"text":"Don't just use them\nbecause they're cheap and easy,"},{"time":355154,"text":"but use them because they're secure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357182,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":358461,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}